name: Juliana Stratton
tweet: Happy #NationalAgDay -- we love our local farmers, growers, processors, and producers!  Agriculture is our state's #1 industry and as Chair of Illinois’ Rural Affairs Council, we're working every day to ensure Illinois leads the nation in agribusiness.

name: Juliana Stratton
tweet: Health care is a right, not a privilege.  @JBPritzker and I won’t rest until every Illinoisan has access to the health care they need -- whether it’s for your mental health, your prescriptions, or your pregnancy.  We’re expanding coverage and lowering costs for all Illinoisans.

name: Juliana Stratton
tweet: Today is #WomenInPublicOfficeDay!  Representation matters and our state government must reflect the diversity that we see in Illinois. To do that, we have to elect more women to office!  I'm proud to partner with @JBPritzker and an administration that champions that belief.
